latestIgtvVideos.title: 💙💙B L U E E Y E S 💙💙
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey, guys hope you all are doing well!!
So here I did blue eyes for this look I have used lake me blue Kajal instead of blue eyeshadow as we all know due to lockdown we are not able to buy beauty products. I tried to create blue eyes look without eyeshadow. I was not sure if these blue eyes look were going to work but it worked! 
Hope you're all staying well and safe💙

Products used
🦋Rosewater @thenaturalwash must buy  you love it best  thing to hydrate your skin 🦋Primer @lovecolorbar 🦋Concealer @lagirlcosmetics I am falling in love with this concealer for a beginner it is worth buying

latestIgtvVideos.title: Makeup Tutorial ❤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
S M O K E Y E Y E S 🖤
Here is my first igtv video of smokey eyes look❤❤❤ I am not a pro make up artist I just wanted to share some of my Quarantine hidden talents this time this is my real happiness and so I thought why not make some productive things.
So here I created smokey eyes look with the use of gel liner 
I haven't used any black eyeshadow to make my eyes smokey you just need a brush or gel liner and any nude eyeshadows pallet to create this smokey eyes

Products mentioned below (I have already applied moisturizer before applying primer )
Don't skip moisturizer before use  primer 
Primer @lovecolorbar
Concealer @lagirlcosmetics
eyeshadows @nyxcosmetics
gel liner @maybelline
mascara @Maybelline 
Kajal @plum
Foundation @maybelline
blush @wetnwildbeauty
highlighter @maybelline
 lipstick 11 bold wine @facescanada
